{"tid":748365,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"gobee.bike「玩完」無退錢　會員轟欺詐","createTime":"2018-07-19T07:06:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-23T12:29:44.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7b6d36ab69ea241657f796a17bb68ac0b5df9c54","tid":748365,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:06:06.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180719/20453912\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180719%2F20453912&d=PmFcvYDdyGly%2FsMPmmCiDRxMMk18geApnjdPrdglKpk%3D&h=04ab649b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180719%2F20453912&h=4701fffa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180719/20453912</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年07月19日 <br />\n<br />\ngobee.bike「玩完」無退錢　會員轟欺詐<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180719/large/19la5p03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180719%2Flarge%2F19la5p03.jpg&h=0a7dfbfe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■gobee.bike昨結束香港業務，近日市面該公司單車數量已大減。徐雲庭攝<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】去年4月引入的本港首間共享單車gobee.bike，上周二突宣佈清盤，並於昨日結束香港業務，只向會員退還按金卻不退充值餘額，會員怒轟此做法形同欺詐，損失數十元至500元不等，消委會及海關均接獲相關投訴。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180719/large/a0503a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180719%2Flarge%2Fa0503a.gif&h=8a76e316&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■會員在網上大呻不夠時間用gobee.bike充值餘額。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區議員質疑違商品例<br />\n<br />\n5月起市面的gobee.bike已大多損壞或無法解鎖，近日單車數量更大減，加上連日落雨，不少會員未能在昨日限期前使用餘額租車。消委會收到54宗投訴，有投訴人稱消委會近日曾發電郵建議他們整理充值紀錄後，聯絡信用卡發卡銀行要求代為討回已預繳的充值額，但不一定成功。<br />\n<br />\n截至昨日下午5時，海關接獲16宗舉報，並正作適當跟進。gobee.bike創辦人Raphael Cohen回覆稱，稍後將移走全港1.7萬架gobee.bike，交由負責清盤的公司處理。他聲稱已完成所有顧客的退款手續，但拒絕退還充值餘額，因當初會員加入時已確認合約條款列明餘額不可退還。<br />\n<br />\n一直跟進gobee.bike及共享單車問題的元朗區議員李月民稱，曾與律師商討，雖然合約條款列明充值餘額不可退還，但在今次事件中未必可作為免責條款，主因是今次公司突然宣佈結束，卻只給予客戶一周使用餘額，時間不足。<br />\n<br />\n此外，李質疑若單車公司決定清盤之後，仍然容許新客開立戶口收取按金及充值，理應退還所有款項給新會員，否則涉嫌違反《商品說明條例》，甚至刑事欺詐。<br />\n<br />\n■記者金敏琍、徐雲庭  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n快運路牌宣傳遭投訴<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n《爆相爆片》七月第二輪揭曉"},{"pid":"8ef896ccea78b7a2517081570ec8a3d3acd91269","tid":748365,"uid":34714,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:06:59.000Z","msg":"仲有五十蚊未用<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d7f3a8d46928b349e1c1d028cd2451e609cf936","tid":748365,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:08:08.000Z","msg":"按金退得晒都好彩"},{"pid":"4707fd5954fdf3976707381ee33bec8fcb23ffa0","tid":748365,"uid":106629,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:09:15.000Z","msg":"[未經證實] 好似有連埋餘額退款<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee324b9653de01cef803353e1acb72d088a03bb8","tid":748365,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:14:13.000Z","msg":"哈哈哈<br />\n<br />\n唔知邊個自私啦今次 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b79ecad9566273341917c64311a5e4c98b434dd","tid":748365,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:34:57.000Z","msg":"綁信用卡扣錢已經唔想用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4c4dfd8bdd20d1ddf17ffc3ea1d399cf7bf82df","tid":748365,"uid":79563,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9b79ecad9566273341917c64311a5e4c98b434dd","tid":748365,"uid":22553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-19T07:34:57.000Z","msg":"綁信用卡扣錢已經唔想用<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci